t/53913/', '', 'Fluocinolone acetonide, Fluorometholone, Fluocinolone acetonide, Fluorometholone, Misoprostol, Chondroitin sulfate, Esomeprazole, Glucosamine, Tolazoline, Dimethyl sulfoxide, Deoxycholic acid, More', '', 1767369485);
